Build-Depends: cmark-gfm <!nodoc>, debhelper-compat (= 13), dh-sequence-rust, librust-anyhow-1+default-dev, librust-clap-4+default-dev, librust-clap-4+derive-dev, librust-serde-1+default-dev, librust-serde-1+derive-dev, librust-serde-yaml-0.9+default-dev, librust-tempfile-3+default-dev, librust-textwrap-0.16+default-dev, librust-thiserror-2+default-dev
Description: graph-based project roadmap modeling - Rust source code roadmap generates directed acyclic graph representations of a project roadmap. The idea is to show the steps needed to reach a goal, and the order they need to be taken, but ignore due dates and other irrelevant details.
Package-List: librust-roadmap-dev deb rust optional arch=all roadmap deb graphics optional arch=any
